1
00:00:01,267 --> 00:00:02,787
Let them decide the ending themselves.

2
00:00:03,970 --> 00:00:04,970
Director...

3
00:00:05,238 --> 00:00:06,718
It's not that I don't have your back,

4
00:00:07,273 --> 00:00:08,273
but isn't this

5
00:00:08,608 --> 00:00:09,743
taking it a bit too far?

6
00:00:12,312 --> 00:00:13,312
So what?

7
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:14,881
I'm just being spontaneous.

8
00:00:15,467 --> 00:00:17,350
Does everything have to follow the script?

9
00:00:17,817 --> 00:00:19,918
Reality shows are all the rage right now.

10
00:00:19,919 --> 00:00:21,955
Why not give it that kind of vibe?

11
00:00:24,791 --> 00:00:26,393
This is Bai Xing's first acting gig.

12
00:00:27,027 --> 00:00:28,528
His manager is worried sick.

13
00:00:29,262 --> 00:00:30,822
And even though Hei Yan has experience,

14
00:00:31,264 --> 00:00:32,904
his manager has been giving me an earful.

15
00:00:33,400 --> 00:00:34,567
Besides,

16
00:00:36,102 --> 00:00:37,570
we're already way over budget.

17
00:00:38,638 --> 00:00:40,339
With so little time left,

18
00:00:40,340 --> 00:00:41,574
are you sure you can finish?

19
00:00:45,211 --> 00:00:46,412
The original script had them

20
00:00:46,413 --> 00:00:47,947
meeting again years later

21
00:00:48,415 --> 00:00:49,916
but not ending up together.

22
00:00:52,919 --> 00:00:54,421
I've always believed

23
00:00:54,988 --> 00:00:56,890
there's a certain beauty in regret.

24
00:01:00,460 --> 00:01:02,328
But watching them on set,

25
00:01:03,196 --> 00:01:04,497
I'm just so curious

26
00:01:05,899 --> 00:01:07,339
to see what they'll actually decide.

27
00:01:14,674 --> 00:01:15,675
Look,

28
00:01:18,845 --> 00:01:19,846
can't you just

29
00:01:20,613 --> 00:01:22,448
be a good sport

30
00:01:22,449 --> 00:01:24,683
and indulge me this once?

31
00:01:24,684 --> 00:01:25,684
Fine.

32
00:01:32,258 --> 00:01:33,860
But if there are any more delays,

33
00:01:34,427 --> 00:01:36,029
it's coming out of your paycheck.

34
00:01:37,330 --> 00:01:38,465
Deal. You said it.

35
00:01:47,106 --> 00:01:48,207
Chen Tianyou,

36
00:01:48,208 --> 00:01:50,143
I broke your bracelet.

37
00:01:50,577 --> 00:01:51,111
But I'm guessing

38
00:01:51,112 --> 00:01:52,578
you didn't really want it back anyway.

39
00:01:52,579 --> 00:01:54,247
"Leaving it with me"?

40
00:01:54,914 --> 00:01:56,749
You were just throwing
it away, weren't you?

41
00:01:58,651 --> 00:01:59,919
I know.

42
00:02:00,954 --> 00:02:03,156
Don't miss me too much, okay?

43
00:02:04,190 --> 00:02:05,458
Don't worry.

44
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:08,360
Okay.
